Utterance.UttText: In bed 15 is William Tran, 81 yrs old under Dr Gabby.
He came in with a severe allergic reaction to bee sting.

Phrase.PhraseText: with a severe allergic reaction to bee sting.

Utterance.UttText: He had swollen airways and he is on IV antihistamine and cortisone.
On oxygen 3l/nasal prongs and on regular pain relief.
He is double incontinent of urine and faeces.
He is otherwise stable and his obs are all within normal limits.
